title: Episode 128: Toot Toot! (Ft. Blac Youngsta & Tip Drill)
itunes:title: Episode 128: Toot Toot! (Ft. Blac Youngsta & Tip Drill)
description:
On this weeks episode, rapper Blac Youngsta sits with the ladies of Lip Service to help them decode typical ‘guy talk.’ Blac Yougsta confesses his love for Lady Gaga as well as the time a woman made him cry. Tip Drill, from Love & Hip Hop Miami rolls through to join in on the conversation!
